      <h2>Intended Use</h2>
      <p>
        This oscillating multi-tool is designed for professional detail sanding, plunge cutting, flush cutting,
        removal of excess material, and surface preparation. <strong>Do not</strong> use it under wet conditions or
        in the presence of flammable liquids or gases. It is a professional power tool &mdash; keep it away from
        children, and supervise inexperienced operators.
      </p>

